quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  16,103,"Kandi rwose tuzi neza ko (ababangikanyamana) bavuga bati \"Mu by’ukuri, hari umuntu umwigisha (iyi Qur’an).\" Ururimi rw’uwo bitirira (ko amwigisha) ni urunyamahanga, nyamara iyi (Qur’an) iri mu rurimi rw’Icyarabu rusobanutse"
  16,104,"Mu by’ukuri, babandi batemera amagambo ya Allah, Allah ntazabayobora kandi bazahanishwa ibihano bibabaza"
  16,105,"Mu by’ukuri, abahimba ikinyoma ni babandi batemera amagambo ya Allah, kandi abo ni bobanyabinyoma"
  16,106,"Uwo ari we wese uhakana Allah nyuma y’uko yemera, (ibihano bikomeye biramutegereje), uretse wawundi uzabihatirwa nyamara umutima we wuje ukwemera. Ariko uwugururira igituza cye ubuhakanyi, abo uburakari bwa Allah buri kuri bo, kandi bazahanishwa ibihano bihambaye"
  16,107,"Ibyo ni ukubera ko bakunze ubuzima bw’isi bakaburutisha ubw’imperuka. Kandi mu by’ukuri, Allah ntayobora abantu b’abahakanyi"
  16,108,"Abo ni babandi Allahyadanangiye imitima yabo, amatwi yabo ndetse n’amaso yabo; kandi abo ni bo barindagiye"
  16,109,Nta gushidikanya ko ari bo bazaba abanyagihombo ku munsi w’imperuka
  16,110,"Naho babandi bimutse nyuma yo gutotezwa, maze bagaharanira inzira ya Allah bakanihangana, nyuma y’ibyo byose, Nyagasani wawe (ku bantu nk’abo) ni Ubabarira ibyaha, Nyirimbabazi"